College of Global Public Health Sustainable Development Goals Master of Public Health

Website for the Sustainable Development Goals concentration for the Master of Public Health program. From 2017-2018, it was considered a separate online master's program. In 2019, it became a concentration. The website contains the core courses, required zero credit courses, concentration courses, electives, and sample course sequences.
